title: intirpritive horse - #Hearts - [mp3 320]
description:
Intirpritive horse started in 2013 in Colorado. Evan Fullmore was on the Drums and Kyle Stersic on Keyboards. #Hearts was made from stitching together samples and recordings compiled over a two year period. The album takes a stab at the Colorado hippy jam band fan / drug dominated live music scene. 

Kyle Stersic - Editing together the whole mess... Sax, EWI, Piano, Keys, Guitars, Tapes, Circuit Bending, Drums, Percussion, Vox, Audio Verite, Editings 

Evan Follmar - Piano, Accordion, Keys, Circuit Bend Yamaha PSS-370, Circuit Bent Drum Machines, Drums, Percussion 

Lige Williamson - Slide Guitar, Vocals 

Justin Avdek - Guitar, Keys, Percussion 

Ryan Fanelli - Bass
